---
layout: default
---
.hero
  .col-xs-12.xy-center.text-center
    .stroke-text
      %h1 Mike & Dan
    %h2 Fast Fixes to Full Features
    %a.btn-ghost{href: "#"} LEARN MORE
.dark-bg
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.text-center
        %h2
          How Can We Help?
        %h3
          Mike & Dan is a tag-team knockout for your business. From front-end to
          back, we'll help make sure your business is running smoothly, and with
          all the modern conveniences today has to offer. Here are some of the
          services we commonly provide:
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/rocketship.png", class: 'img-responsive'}
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Website and Mobile Launch
        %h3
          We like to build <u>responsive</u>, <u>fast</u>, and <u>accessible</u>
          websites that are an extension of you and your business. And we like
          to turn those websites into mobile apps! That way you and your
          customers can connect anywhere and everywhere.
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Laser-Focused Optimizations
        %h3
          Good software is about knowing what to do. We only start work on a
          project after we've worked with you to identify <u>exactly</u>
          where we can provide value. That way you can grow your business
          <u>without</u> the cost of a full-time developer.
      .col-md-3.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/magnifyglass.png", class: 'img-responsive'}
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/conveyor.png", class: 'img-responsive', style: 'padding-top: 10px;'}
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Automated Business Services
        %h3
          Beyond getting your business online, we aim to get your <i>business
          processes</i> online. Using cloud automation we can get your business'
          logistics organized and digitized, leaving you free to focus on your
          customer's experience.
    %hr
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.text-center
          %h4
            And more! Each situation is unique, and we like to recommend the
            best tool for the job. Contact us today to setup your first
            consultation session.
          %form#contactform.form-horizontal{method: "POST"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Name:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "name", type: "text"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Email:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "_replyto", type: "email"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Business:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "business", type: "email"}
            .form-group
              .col-sm-2
                %label Info:
              .col-sm-10
                %textarea.form-control{name: "notes", rows: "3"}
            %input{name: "_gotcha", style: "display:none", type: "text"}/
            %input.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{type: "submit", value: "Submit"}
          :javascript
            var contactform =  document.getElementById('contactform');
            contactform.setAttribute('action', '//formspree.io/' + 'info' + '@' + 'getmikeanddan' + '.' + 'com');
    %hr
